{title: Aleluya · Todo el mundo debe saberlo}
{artist: Genverde}
{key: G}

{soc}
[G]Aleluya, [C]aleluya,[G] a[Em]le[D]lu[C]ya,
[G]Aleluya, [C]aleluya,[G] a[Em]le[D]lu[C]ya,
